\c 23
\s Jehovha mufudzi wangu
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha mufudzi wangu; handishaiwi.
\v 2 Anondirarisa pamafuro manyoro; anondisesedza pamvura inozorodza.
\v 3 Anovandudza mweya wangu; anondisesedza panzira dzekururama nekuda kwezita rake.
\v 4 Hongu, kunyange ndikafamba nemumupata wemumvuri werufu, handingatyi chakaipa, nokuti imwi muneni; tsvimbo yenyu nemudonzvo wenyu, ndizvo zvinondinyaradza.
\v 5 Munogadzira tafura mberi kwangu pamberi pevavengi vangu; munozodza musoro wangu nemafuta; mukombe wangu unopfachuka.
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo kunaka nenyasha zvichanditevera mazuva ese eupenyu hwangu; uye ndichagara mumba maJehovha kusvika paurefu hwemazuva.